window.bookSummaryJSON = "Diana Gabaldon, the number-one <i>New York Times</i> best-selling author of the Outlander saga and a Quill Award winner, delivers a treat for her many fans - a collection of three novellas starring the ever-popular Lord John Grey. <p>In these tales, Lord John vows to avenge a murder, investigates a terrifying \"night-hag\" on the battlefields of Europe, and discovers treason in His Majesty's ranks.</p>"; 
